panels.title: Multimedia Net Kibana
panels.content:
### Welcome to Multimedia Net. 

You can change and update these dashboards to match your needs. 

 1. [Business view](index.html#/dashboard/file/Business_view.json) *Provide KPI about Business* 
 2. [Integration view](index.html#/dashboard/file/Integration_view.json) *Provide details about integration metrics* 
 3. [Technical view](index.html#/dashboard/file/Technical_view.json) *Provide details about Operating system* 
 4. 

 You can also create your own dashboards from scratch, for monitoring of your own application, BAM, etc. 
 To do this, you can start from: 
 1. [Blank dashboard](index.html#/dashboard/file/blank.json) 
 2. [Simple dashboard](index.html#/dashboard/file/guided.json)
